---

<Page title="Project">
  <h2 class="mt-10 uppercase title-decoration">Latest</h2>
  <section class="project-content">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.4em">
      <a class="project-title-link" href={`https://howdz.vercel.app`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Howdz 🔸 浏览器起始页
        <svg class="outlink-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M10 3v2H5v14h14v-5h2v6a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h6zm7.586 2H13V3h8v8h-2V6.414l-7 7L10.586 12l7-7z"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </h3>
    <div class="outlink-wrapper">
      {dashboardLink.map(item => <a href={item.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{item.name}</a>)}
    </div>
    <div class="description-wrapper">
      完全自定义配置的浏览器导航首页面板，支持自定义添加天气、时钟、搜索、收藏等各种物料组件，可编辑删除组件与其各种样式或功能属性。响应式设计，可自定义随机壁纸背景图或动态壁纸。
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="project-content">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.4em">
      <a class="project-title-link" href={`https://kongfandong.cn/howdy/`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Howdyjs 🔸 插件库
        <svg class="outlink-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M10 3v2H5v14h14v-5h2v6a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h6zm7.586 2H13V3h8v8h-2V6.414l-7 7L10.586 12l7-7z"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </h3>
    <div class="outlink-wrapper">
      {howdyLink.map(item => <a href={item.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{item.name}</a>)}
    </div>
    <div class="description-wrapper">
      个人JS插件库，包含自定义拖拽、滚动条、右键菜单、图片放大等原生JS插件和动画模态框、标签页等Vue3组件或指令。
    </div>
    <details>
      <summary>组件列表</summary>
      <ul class="howdy-component">
        {
          howdyComponent.map(item =>
            <li>
              <a href={item.link} target="_blank">{item.title}</a>
              <p>{item.text}</p>
            </li>
          )
        }
      </ul>
    </details>
  </section>

  <h2 class="mt-10 uppercase title-decoration">Other</h2>
  <section class="project-content">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.4em">
      <a class="project-title-link" href={`https://kongfandong.cn/coder/`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        💻 Code Editor - 在线代码IDE
        <svg class="outlink-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M10 3v2H5v14h14v-5h2v6a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h6zm7.586 2H13V3h8v8h-2V6.414l-7 7L10.586 12l7-7z"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </h3>
    <div class="outlink-wrapper">
      {coderLink.map(item => <a href={item.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{item.name}</a>)}
    </div>
    <div class="description-wrapper">
      基于Vue3实现的一个仿<code>CodePen</code>的在线代码IDE，响应式布局支持移动端，可拖拽更改页面布局。另支持<code>Sass</code>语法、<code>Emmet</code>快输、自动刷新等。
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="project-content">
    <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.4em">
      <a class="project-title-link" href={`https://leon-kfd.github.io/g-music-visualizer/`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        🎵 Music Visualizer - 音乐可视化方案
        <svg class="outlink-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path d="M10 3v2H5v14h14v-5h2v6a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H4a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V4a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h6zm7.586 2H13V3h8v8h-2V6.414l-7 7L10.586 12l7-7z"></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </h3>
    <div class="outlink-wrapper">
      {musicVisualizerLink.map(item => <a href={item.link} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">{item.name}</a>)}
    </div>
    <div class="description-wrapper">
      利用<code>G</code>渲染器与React制作的一个音乐可视化方案，基于AudioContext的decodeAudioDataAPI读取音频数据，可以随机获取一首歌曲体验多种可视化效果。
    </div>
  </section>
</Page>
